ca, Philippe Grosperrin, Vittorio Grigolo"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b3247e7dbc632a4b9e79d7e45fbef703" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Jocelyne-De-Nicola-130x200.jpg" width="65" height="100" alt="Jocelyne De Nicola" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Jocelyne De Nicola"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/jocelyne-de-nicola/">View all articles by Jocelyne De Nicola</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/07/xxxviii-festival-della-valle-ditria-artaserse-di-hasse/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> XXXVIII° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;Artaserse&#8221; di Hasse</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/07/il-balletto-di-san-pietroburgo-ne-il-lago-dei-cigni/" rel="next">Il Balletto di San Pietroburgo ne &#8220;Il lago dei cigni&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-15390"> <article id="comment-15390" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ed96c087bbdf553346b8dc4ee9fec170?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">michele.macaluso@fastwebnet.it</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/07/la-boheme-alla-choregies-orange/#comment-15390"><time datetime="2012-07-18T10:34:43+00:00">18 luglio 2012 at 10:34</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Leggendo la presentazione dell&#8217;opera si evince che è stata una Bohème scarsa e mediocre. Come sempre il lato negativo è la solita regia paranoica e modernista a tutti i costi. Caos aggiungerei gran casino.L&#8217;intimismo dell&#8217;opera pucciniana diventa un inutile colossal ed i cantanti  si saranno sicuramente smarriti e pertanto le loro prestazioni si sono rivolte contro di loro in modo logicamente negativo. La morte di Mimì mi fa proprio ridere per non dire piangere.Quando potremo ancora vedere una Bohéme al naturale con i dettami di Giacosa e Illica?. E&#8217; proprio necessario affidarsi ai soliti registi dai cachet esagewati ma privi come sempre ed in ogni altro Teatro della giusta misura che solo la tradizione può arridere ad un certo e sicuro successo!</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2012/07/la-boheme-alla-choregies-orange/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_post_ID' value='37680' id='comment_post_ID' /> <input type='hidden' name='comment_parent' id='comment_parent' value='0' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="aa41892f6d" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="97"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedpo